main event: A very bright circular object was seen moving across the sky over Chevy Chase, Maryland, on March 23, 1963.
interesting points: The object was observed for over two hours as it traversed across several states,The object was described as having a glowing, fiery corona and was larger than the full moon,The motion of the object on the ground was accompanied by a whirlwind approximately 50 feet in diameter, multiple eyewitnesses reported seeing the object, The incident was later investigated by the Franklin Institute, which deemed the object an unidentified flying object.
sighted object: a bright circular object with a fiery corona
